Package data.transfer.updater

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationUpdateChecker
    Has the responsibility to check the applications version files on the FTP repository, and check if it is more recent than the local ones.
    ApplicationUpdateData
    Simple wrapper class for data required when updating an application.
    ApplicationUpdateDataDeserializer
    JSON deserializer for ApplicationUpdateData objects.
    ApplicationUpdater
    Handles basic coordination for the update of one application.
    ApplicationUpdateService
    Service that handles downloading an application applicationExecutable from the remote FTP repository.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ApplicationExecutable
    Represents one of the executables of the Arcadoid suite.
